{
  "texts": [
    "Below, we introduce each step in detail.",
    "In the \"Plan\" step of DevOps, teams define project goals, requirements, and timelines.",
    "This phase establishes the initial roadmap for the project, involving activities such as gathering user stories, prioritizing features, and assigning tasks.",
    "During this phase, the team identifies project objectives and security needs, engaging in threat modeling to grasp security vulnerabilities and plan security measures accordingly [197].",
    "Furthermore, software impact analysis is conducted to identify entities directly or indirectly influenced by a change [9]."
  ]
}